TP/1.1 200 OK\r\n< content-length: 2074\r\n< last-modified: Sun, 03 May 2020 09:48:08 GMT\r\n< accept-ranges: bytes\r\n< content-type: text/html\r\n< etag: \"114457b:81a:5eae9358:73e1149\"\r\n< content-disposition: inline; filename=\"index.html\"\r\n< date: Sat, 09 May 2020 07:17:32 GMT\r\n```\r\n\r\nAsk for the first part of the file (It's important here, because of `offset != 0` condition in the code):\r\n```\r\ncurl -r 0-20 -vvv 'http://0.0.0.0:8081/static/index.html' > /dev/null\r\n> GET /static/index.html HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: 0.0.0.0:8081\r\n> Range: bytes=0-20\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.70.0\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> \r\n* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse\r\n< HTTP/1.1 206 Partial Content\r\n< transfer-encoding: chunked\r\n< last-modified: Sun, 03 May 2020 09:48:08 GMT\r\n< accept-ranges: bytes\r\n< content-type: text/html\r\n< content-range: bytes 0-20/2074\r\n< etag: \"114457b:81a:5eae9358:73e1149\"\r\n< content-disposition: inline; filename=\"index.html\"\r\n< date: Sat, 09 May 2020 07:17:37 GMT\r\n```\r\n\r\nAsk for any other part of the file:\r\n```\r\ncurl -r 10-20 -vvv 'http://0.0.0.0:8081/static/index.html' > /dev/null\r\n> GET /static/index.html HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: 0.0.0.0:8081\r\n> Range: bytes=10-20\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.70.0\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> \r\n* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse\r\n< HTTP/1.1 206 Partial Content\r\n< transfer-encoding: chunked\r\n< last-modified: Sun, 03 May 2020 09:48:08 GMT\r\n< accept-ranges: bytes\r\n< content-type: text/html\r\n< content-range: bytes 10-20/2074\r\n< etag: \"114457b:81a:5eae9358:73e1149\"\r\n< content-disposition: inline; filename=\"index.html\"\r\n< date: Sat, 09 May 2020 07:17:41 GMT\r\n```\r\n\r\n**After my changes:**\r\n\r\nAsk for the whole file:\r\n```\r\ncurl -vvv 'http://0.0.0.0:8081/static/index.html' > /dev/null\r\n> GET /static/index.html HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: 0.0.0.0:8081\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.70.0\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> \r\n* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse\r\n< HTTP/1.1 200 OK\r\